  U7 1-kang, in ang chhut-goa7 cho3 seng-li2, iau2-boe7 tng2--lai5, jit8-thau5 1-e7 am3, koh u7 siau2 ti-ko lai5 chhoe7 I--a. I m7-kaN2 tiam2 lah8-hoe2, chhu3-lai7 am3 bin-bong, chham khe3-hiaN leh chhin-jiat8 e5 si5, ma7 m7-chai hit-e5 lang5 si7 chng-thau5 e5 po2-cheng3, iah-si7 keh-piah chng e5 chng-tiuN2? 
